{
  "stem": "20684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The money run out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got kicked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was secret.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think my-- my mother-- well, my mother has never spoken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She's still alive, in a nursing home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She is 92 years old, not in all her capacities, but nevertheless.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she has never spoken about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It stopped in '39.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It starts in '45.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Blank.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If her life depended on it, she would not say a single thing about the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She didn't have it all that easy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyhow, once we got kicked out of the cupboard, we started wandering around the forest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Were given a bundle of food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We started wandering around the forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Was dark, night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And suddenly the most fascinating things that ever happened to me in my life, and I've had a 61-year-old life, the light suddenly-- something happened.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a crack somewhere down there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I could see something happening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now, I hadn't seen light for just over a year, which is a quarter of my life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it seems like a long time to be in the darkness, as you probably know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A year is a long time in-- in anyone's life, but in a child life it's even longer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Suddenly the light started coming out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was getting excited, started jumping up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then I think I wee'd myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And my father told me to put my hands on my-- on my eyes, because I will go blind.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But, of course, even then I was already crook.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I've been crook ever since, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I'm a-- I'm a-- cannot be trusted, I should say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I'm not a thief, but I can't be trusted, as they-- people say.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I would slip my eye-- my-- my fingers, and-- and I would see that sunrise.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
